      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; constitutive model selection documented.",
      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was selected based on literature precedent for CFD blood trauma applications. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2."
