      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; nominal input values sourced from published literature.",
      "rationale": "Fluid properties and hemolysis model constants were taken from peer-reviewed sources. Sensitivity analysis on inputs is not mandated at MRL 2. Factor held at level 1."
    },
    {
