      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; dimensional similarity between validation and deployment conditions documented qualitatively.",
      "rationale": "Dimensional analysis confirms that the validation Reynolds number range (Re 1200–4800) overlaps with the CPB clinical operating regime. Full equivalency mapping is not required at MRL 2."
    }
