    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to level 1 per MRL 2 requirements and are not assessed, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Note: this submission conforms to the Minimal profile; a structured Context of Use object is not included in this package version.",
